    {
      "id": "53db1b8d-15b5-4301-8393-afe43ae1d8a9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Model achieves more than 90% accuracy, greatly outperforming Logistic Regression or SVM models. Including Legacy Data AND Assessment-related data greatly impacts the performance of a model. Also, students who go back to check previous lectures also seem to perform better.\n\n",
